# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Generic kernel:       ~50-80 MB bzImage + ~800MB-1.2GB modules
# Native minimal build: ~15-20 MB bzImage + ~80-150MB modules
# 
# Savings: ~85-92% reduction in disk footprint
